Step 2: Tauri IPC commands implementation

New modules:
  - commands/open_file.rs: open file, parse conflicts, get BASE from git
  - commands/resolve.rs: resolve single conflict by ID (Local/Remote/Both/Manual)
  - commands/magic_merge.rs: auto-resolve non-conflicting changes
  - commands/save.rs: build resolved content, write to file with .bak backup
  - commands/get_base.rs: fetch BASE version via git2
  - lib.rs: register all 5 commands + Mutex<Option<MergeSession>> state mgmt

Improvements:
  - save.rs uses lexer::detect_marker for robust conflict block replacement
  - ConflictMarkers and fields made pub for cross-module reuse
  - Unused session_id warnings fixed (_session_id prefix)
  - All 15 parser tests still pass; cargo check clean
